"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Shape Sue’s personality, behavior, and appearance through your actions and decisions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>High-quality visuals</strong>: Thousands of hand-crafted 3D renders and hundreds of animations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>6–8 hours of gameplay per kink path</strong>: Over <strong>18+ hours total</strong> if you explore every route.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">In-game phone with social media, text messages, Photo mode, and unlockable galleries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Original soundtrack and immersive sound effects.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2579730/extras/76dfcacf7a98d64fca075806b519f8f2.poster.avif?t=1773060610\" width=616 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2579730/extras/76dfcacf7a98d64fca075806b519f8f2.webm?t=1773060610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2579730/extras/76dfcacf7a98d64fca075806b519f8f2.mp4?t=1773060610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>What NOT to Expect</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">This is <strong>not</strong> a sandbox or a 3D open-world game. It's a fully scripted visual novel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You <strong>won't be able to customize the characters</strong>' body types—this is a curated experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">There is no Voice Acting in game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Not a vanilla romance. Expect <strong>kink